Entities Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 115).</history-note>
          <history-note id="DLM55703"><amended-provision>Section 22(2)(d)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>repealed</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM331111">section 200</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Crown
Entities Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 115).</history-note>
          <history-note id="DLM55704"><amended-provision>Section 22(3)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>substituted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>25 January 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM331111">section 200</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Crown
Entities Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 115).</history-note>
        </history>
      </notes>
    </prov>
